        <body>       
                
                <pb n="1"/>
            <p>Tremont. Popham St.<lb/>
                Nov 2 1888<lb/></p>
            <p>My dear Doctor Morais&#44;<lb/></p>
            <p>I am in receipt of your letter<lb/> Nov. 1<hi rend="sup">st</hi>.  It affords me much pleasure&#44;<lb/> and relief&#59; to know that my efforts as far<lb/> as you have been able to inform yourself&#44;<lb/> are approved&#44; <del>by your</del><lb/></p>
            <p>I send you the rough copy<lb/> of my &#34;<hi rend="underline">Index</hi>.&#34;&#45;&#45;&#34;<hi rend="underline">appendix</hi>&#44; <hi rend="underline">and notes</hi>.&#45;&#45;that<lb/> you may be able to see the scope of the<lb/> work&#44; and <del>be able</del> to appreciate the object&#44;<lb/> which has <hi rend="underline">prompted</hi> me to devote so much<lb/> time labor and research&#44; to what&#44; <hi rend="underline">some think &#34;Waste of time</hi>&#34;<lb/></p> 
            <p>I have supplied all the <hi rend="underline">Literature</hi> both<lb/> <hi rend="underline">Sacred</hi> and <hi rend="underline">profane</hi>&#44; to enable the reader to refer<lb/> for proof without resorting to <hi rend="underline">Libraries</hi>&#44; where<lb/> all the Subject treated <hi rend="underline">might not be found</hi>.<lb/></p>
            <p>I shall not use your letter to me until<lb/> you have perused the <hi rend="underline">Index. of contents</hi>&#44; as<lb/> you may have expressed yourself in it more<lb/> <hi rend="underline">flatteringly</hi> than I deserve&#44;&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>If Dr Jastrow is in town and you like<lb/> to show him the &#34;Content&#44;&#34; and communicate<lb/> what you know about the book&#44; <hi rend="underline">do so</hi>&#44; and it<lb/></p>
                
                <pb n="2"/>
            <p>will increase my obligations to you.&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>I should like to have the MSS back<lb/> as it will take considerable time to make<lb/> another condensation.&#45;&#45;<lb/></p>
            <p>I am my dear Doctor<lb/>
                Yours Very Truly<lb/>
                S. N. Carvalho.&#45;<lb/></p>
            </body>
    </text>
